text: Cancellaria crenulata is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. This has become a nomen dubium (invalid: junior homonym of Cancellaria crenulata Deshayes, 1835) ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== * Hemmen J. (2007) Recent Cancellariidae.
